Enum CardUpdateType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CardUpdateType>
      • app.model.CardUpdateType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CardUpdateType>

    public enum CardUpdateType
extends java.lang.Enum<CardUpdateType>
    The CardUpdateType enumeration defines actions that are done on cards. They are passed in model:notifyObserver() to inform the view to do the similar action with its ViewCards

    v0.6
